{"tid":1541952,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"所有海外學生同我入嚟，你地至少仲可以做到一樣野","createTime":"2019-09-04T16:58:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T17:52:52.000Z","uid":97350,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"50626662420bda3676a20efcd4644b5bd8e87ce1","tid":1541952,"uid":97350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:58:37.000Z","msg":"好多海外巴絲可能好似我咁，唔出去集會，唔做booth，唔搞Lennon wall，冇朋友，冇人傾到反送中，日日上連登做鍵盤戰士。<br />\n喺香港人快速進化嘅情況下，你可能會覺得好無力，覺得自己咩都做唔到，好抑鬱。<br />\n但我同你地講你哋仲有一樣野可以做！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>尋日淋病突然間宣布&rdquo;動議&rdquo;撤回修例，唔係驚左香港人，而係驚左美國嘅人權法案，所以我哋要更加利用國外輿論，煲大件事佢。</strong></span><br />\n每間大學(好似係)其實都有免費心理輔導Counselling and Psychological Services。只要你係學生就可以book in，以我嘅大學為例佢地通常會比6個section你，你就有1個鐘同佢傾下計。<br />\n唔好以為外國人咩都知，其實唔係個個都睇國際新聞，有啲真係連黃之鋒係乜水都唔知。但無論咩國家嘅人都好，都有一個共通點，就係相信民主自由，所以只要你同佢地講佢地都會relate到。<br />\n唔好覺得咁做冇用，依家香港留學頭幾個選擇都係英美澳加紐，英美幾重要就唔洗講啦。澳洲係全世界數一數二multi cultural 嘅國家(我Counsellor係歐洲人)，仲要大部分人都唔妥大陸，你同佢一個講，佢又同佢啲fd講，一傳十，十傳百。<br />\n加拿大算係中國人最早移民去嘅國家，啲蝗多到數唔曬，啲人幾憎佢地可想而知。<br />\n就算你唔係為左想傳開去，揾個人傾下都對你mental health有好處。喺資訊爆炸嘅年代，你好容易會比資訊overwhelmed ，導致reactive depression，搞到你精神緊張，訓唔到，發惡夢等。塭個唔識嘅人傾下計，屌下共狗，抒發下情緒，亦唔一定淨係講香港嘅情況，講下自己，唔單止提高international awareness，仲可以調整自己心理狀態。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命。<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可。</span></span>"},{"pid":"f98dc0ab9b1ae3462bb3adfef0c91c90f2f6e06f","tid":1541952,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:59:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">撤LLM 對準政權</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNutjAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNutjAi.jpg&h=1817afe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">得到黨媒認證</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi 赤納粹</span></span></strong><br />\nChinazi就係China+Nazi。<br />\n赤=共產紅色恐怖, 納粹不解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 全民反共 對準政權！</span></span></strong><br />\n黑警、黨鐵，港共全部都係人民既敵人<br />\n而背後一直有一個終極大Boss中共<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻中共絕對係十個煲得兩個蓋，準備爆煲。<br />\n今日唔號召世界圍堵中共，更待何時？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用#Chinazi黎connect全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. Connect所有黃絲。</span></strong><br />\n殘酷既現實係，並唔係所有黃絲都支持勇武。但黃絲最驚就係共產黨打到黎，一於用反共connect呢班淺黃!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"967d80e831740609615bc253e1dbecc03426fdea","tid":1541952,"uid":97350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:09:09.000Z","msg":"Push比多啲人睇，心靈好脆弱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62407165e19a77b6e49b4bfb93c3b05a8637f66d","tid":1541952,"uid":136299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:12:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38e23aa6f70b12319fb8f1f208134407d13d7dfc","tid":1541952,"uid":40776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:13:16.000Z","msg":"推！<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"2fd54f6ba4a3eff153df262bd4302eae7773bbfd","tid":1541952,"uid":97350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:21:56.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"58eb02f0d7a43b63772754d2ad420af74162c9be","tid":1541952,"uid":97350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T22:40:46.000Z","msg":"正經po都冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b70c1f55f8cae023493b4f254d366a59125b301","tid":1541952,"uid":86277,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T23:12:37.000Z","msg":"又真係冇諗到有呢步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n攞正牌捉住佢講幾個鐘<br />\n<br />\n係咪要同佢講明話唔介意佢同人講<br />\n唔係佢可能基於client私隱，輪到佢屈住屈住"},{"pid":"dc168cd6573869af42ef4e9b8fa01f2ca9a660f7","tid":1541952,"uid":97350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b70c1f55f8cae023493b4f254d366a59125b301","tid":1541952,"uid":86277,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T23:12:37.000Z","msg":"又真係冇諗到有呢步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n攞